	<key>readme</key>
	<string># Feral AI

Alfred workflow for reusable AI prompts. Each prompt walks you through a
guided series of fields, then copies the fully-assembled prompt to the
clipboard.

Add or edit prompts in prompts.json (+ a template file in prompts/) and
run ./rebuild.sh to regenerate info.plist.

Prompts: see prompts.json.
</string>
